# Generated clips, audio, renders and temp files go here.
# Sub-directories are created at runtime by each pipeline stage.
#
# Structure:
#   outputs/clips/    — per-scene MP4 clips from video_gen
#   outputs/audio/    — per-scene WAV + full narration from audio_gen
#   outputs/renders/  — final assembled MP4 from post_prod
#   outputs/tmp/      — concat lists, intermediate files
